Thence S 43° 29' 05" E, along the southwesterly line of said 1.710 acre tract, along said northeasterly LA/RW and said 2.584 acre tract and along a new City of Columbus Corporation Line (Case No. #ANX-24-23, Ord. No. 2427-2023, I.N. 202311010114473), 66.6± feet to an angle point thereof and being at the northwesterly comer of a 6.11 acre tract of land conveyed to the Board of County Commissioners of Franklin County, Ohio, by deed recorded in Deed Book 3078, Page 46, originally appropriated to the State of Ohio as part of a 5.88 acre tract of land designated as Parcel 54-WD (FRA-33-(26.21-30.13)) in Franklin County Court of Common Pleas Case No. 213730; 
